  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This technique can be used on a target held by Sabaku Kyuu or Sabaku Rou, and immediately dispels it after this technique finishes.<br><br>If the target is entangled by Sabaku Kyuu, it suffers 6d6 damage, and the affected limb becomes unusable until regenerated or healed by the likes of Iryou Ninjutsu: Hiken - Nikuteki Taisha. If it's immobilized by Sabaku Kyuu or held by Sabaku Rou, it suffers 6d10 damage instead, and must make a save against massive damage. In either case, a successful save halves the damage.<br><br>If the target is held within a sphere created by Sabaku Rou, you can perform this technique without meeting its Perform Requirements, and can empower it for 1 additional die of damage at the cost of 2 Chakra (maximum 12 total dice). A target held by Sabaku Rou counts as though immobilized by sand.<br><br>If the target is @Condition[disabled]{disabled} or starts dying due to this technique, it suffers 2d6 Strength damage (Fortitude halves).</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
